Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.57,0:22:11.03,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Let's hang out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.66,0:22:15.62,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}I wanna talk with you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.83,0:22:19.63,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}待ち合わせは何時？（10時）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.88,0:22:21.80,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}駅前に集合（OK！）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.92,0:22:25.38,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}着いたら教えて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.51,0:22:27.30,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}使い慣れたスタンプで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.55,0:22:29.93,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}話合えちゃうスタンスが本当
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.14,0:22:33.68,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}心地良くて愛しい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.18,0:22:37.73,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}一人胸にしまいこんだ言葉も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.35,0:22:41.98,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}上手くいかない減らない悩み事も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.36,0:22:48.41,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}全部忘れて遊びに行きたいね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.82,0:22:54.91,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}心のメモリア
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.91,0:22:58.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}笑顔が溢れるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.29,0:23:02.21,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}冗談混じりで頷く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.42,0:23:06.13,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}何気ないありふれたやり取りが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.30,0:23:11.34,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}心のメモリア
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.34,0:23:14.43,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}涙が零れても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.72,0:23:16.93,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}頑張れるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.93,0:23:20.65,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}君がくれた今日が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.90,0:23:23.48,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}優しくてありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.48,0:23:24.94,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Let's hang out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.53,0:23:29.36,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}I wanna talk with you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.83,0:22:19.63,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}约好的时间是几点（十点）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.88,0:22:21.80,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}在车站前集合（OK）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.92,0:22:25.38,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}到了就告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.51,0:22:27.30,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}能够拿用惯了的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.55,0:22:29.93,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}来交谈心事的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.14,0:22:33.68,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}实在让人舒心爱怜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.18,0:22:37.73,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}独自藏在自己心里的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.35,0:22:41.98,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}过得不顺 越来越多的烦心事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.36,0:22:48.41,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}想要全都忘掉 和你一起出去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.82,0:22:54.91,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}留在心中的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.91,0:22:58.00,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}是洋溢在脸上的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.29,0:23:02.21,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}是半开玩笑的点头
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.42,0:23:06.13,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}是不经意间毫不稀奇的交谈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.30,0:23:11.34,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}留在心中的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.34,0:23:14.43,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}哪怕泪水夺眶而出
